OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FWords by Emily Youlton, Senior
OL,7,FPolitics Producer
OL,9,FA defence minister has suggested that
OL,10,FAndy Burnham only found out about the
OL,11,F#4.7 billion black hole in the defence
OL,12,Finvestment plan (Dip) on the day it
OL,13,Fwas published.
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer announced an extra
OL,16,F#15 billion of spending over the next
OL,17,Ffour years to upgrade the military but
OL,18,Fthe Treasury put off setting out full
OL,19,Fdetails of how it would fund the
OL,20,Fincrease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
