FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FDefence Secretary Dan Jarvis is facing
OL,7,Fquestions over the funding gap and
OL,8,Fwhether Burnham, who is expected to
OL,9,Freplace Keir as prime minister, was
OL,10,Fblindsided by the need to plug it in
OL,11,Fhis first budget.
OL,13,FSpeaking to broadcasters, Jarvis said:
OL,14,F"It's entirely routine that in major
OL,15,Fcommittals of resource that some of
OL,16,Fthe money will be allocated in the
OL,17,Fnext budget or next spending review."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FIt's believed that Burnham did know
OL,7,Fabout the bulk of the defence plans
OL,8,Freleased on Tuesday as part of ongoing
OL,9,Faccess talks with the civil service
OL,10,Fbut this nearly #5 billion funding gap
OL,11,Fwas not discussed.
OL,13,FWhat is a funding black hole?
OL,15,F"Black hole" has almost become a
OL,16,Ftrademark phrase of this Labour
OL,17,Fgovernment, with their continued
OL,18,Freference to the #22 billion black
OL,19,Fhole left by the previous Conservative
OL,20,Fpremiership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FThe term refers to a funding
OL,7,Fshortfall, where spend had been
OL,8,Fcommitted or even required by
OL,9,Fgovernment departments to continue
OL,10,Ftheir work and cope with general
OL,11,Finflation.
OL,13,FHow does the defence funding work?
OL,15,FUnder the government's current fiscal
OL,16,Frules, national debt must "be falling
OL,17,Fas a share of the economy" meaning
OL,18,Fthat the government try to avoid
OL,19,Fborrowing wherever possible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FStarmer has previously said he will
OL,7,Fnot borrow to fund defence but has
OL,8,Frefused to rule out tax rises.
OL,10,FThe funding uplift announced on
OL,11,FTuesday promised an additional #15
OL,12,Fbillion for the military on top of the
OL,13,Fcurrent Ministry of Defence budget,
OL,14,Ftaking it to around #289 billion, but
OL,15,F#4.7 billion of that funding is not
OL,16,Fyet secured.
OL,18,FThe money secured so far is from
OL,19,Freductions in other department's
OL,20,Fspending, sale of government assets,
OL,21,Fand more effective procurement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FThe government confirmed that
OL,7,F"departments have been asked to
OL,8,Fcontribute 1p in every #1 of their
OL,9,Fcapital budgets from this year".
OL,11,FIn his speech on Tuesday, Starmer said
OL,12,Fsome areas like "roads and energy"
OL,13,Fwill not "go ahead as planned" so that
OL,14,Fthe defence target can be met.
OL,16,FThe Department for Transport (DfT) and
OL,17,FDepartment for Energy Security and Net
OL,18,FZero (DESNZ) have been asked to make
OL,19,Fgreater contributions as they have
OL,20,Flarger budgets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FThe DfT has to make savings of up to
OL,7,F#700m from roads funding and DESNZ #2
OL,8,Fbillion of savings while still driving
OL,9,Fforward the plans for renewable energy
OL,10,Fand net zero.
OL,12,FSince then, there has been backlash
OL,13,Fover the cancelled projects, including
OL,14,Ffrom foreign office minister Hamish
OL,15,FFalconer who expressed his upset over
OL,16,Fthe cuts to road improvements in his
OL,17,Fconstituency of Lincoln and across to
OL,18,Fthe East Midlands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
