PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FHe took to social media writing a
OL,7,Fstatement which said: "I am
OL,8,Fdisappointed by the uncertainty today
OL,9,Fabout the A46 Newark bypass-widening
OL,10,Fscheme."
OL,12,FNewark MP Robert Jenrick also
OL,13,Fexpressed his fury and said the road
OL,14,Fexpansion was "an important project
OL,15,Ffor the area has been thrown into
OL,16,Fdisarray".
OL,26,@oD@WOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
