PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FBut this is how the funding will work,
OL,7,Fother departments have to sacrifice
OL,8,Ftheir spend in order to fund defence,
OL,9,Fespecially as borrowing has been ruled
OL,10,Fout currently.
OL,12,FIt's either that or tax rises.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FWhat does it mean for Andy Burnham?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FThe defence secretary said on
OL,7,FWednesday that he has "the assurance
OL,8,Fthat as prime minister Andy Burnham
OL,9,Fwill make sure that we have got the
OL,10,Finvestment coming into defence".
OL,12,FBut the question is, how will Burnham
OL,13,Factually find that money and what does
OL,14,Fit mean for the start of his potential
OL,15,Fpremiership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FBurnham has previously said he will
OL,7,Fretain Rachel Reeves' fiscal rules
OL,8,Fwhich means he won't borrow to plug
OL,9,Fthe funding gap but has not been
OL,10,Fparticularly clear on his plans for
OL,11,Fdefence policy.
OL,13,FThe likely new Labour leader had
OL,14,Fpushed Starmer to delay the release of
OL,15,FDip, so that Burnham could tackle the
OL,16,Fchallenge himself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FBut the outgoing PM pressed ahead in
OL,7,Fwhat is seen as a legacy project
OL,8,Fdelivering the "most significant
OL,9,Fupgrade in defence spending since the
OL,10,F1980's".
OL,12,FBurnham and his new cabinet will have
OL,13,Fto look at what else they can do to
OL,14,Fsave money in order to continue this
OL,15,Fcommitment to defence spending and
OL,16,Fwill need to factor this into his
OL,17,Ffirst budget or spending review.
OL,19,FSpeculation continues over Burnham's
OL,20,Fpick for Chancellor, with Ed Miliband
OL,21,Fa rumoured front runner for the job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FIf he were to become leader of the
OL,7,FTreasury, he may not be as keen to cut
OL,8,Fmore funding from DESNZ, his current
OL,9,Fdepartment.
OL,11,FThe other option could be to cut the
OL,12,Fwelfare bill, with current forecasts
OL,13,Fshowing the government spending #333.7
OL,14,Fbillion on welfare for the 2025-2026
OL,15,Ffinancial year, an increase from
OL,16,F#314.9 billion from the last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782908305
OL,3,CHow the black hole in new defence plan
OL,4,Cwill cause problems for Burnham
OL,6,FBurnham has previously said he wants
OL,7,Fto invest in people getting back into
OL,8,Fwork to reduce the bill, but bigger
OL,9,Fwelfare cuts would likely cause him
OL,10,Fdifficulty with the left of the party,
OL,11,Fwho previously revolted against
OL,12,FStarmer's reforms on this.
OL,14,FStarting a premiership with a black
OL,15,Fhole looming is not what any
OL,16,Fprospective prime minister would want
OL,17,Fbut it's looking increasingly likely
OL,18,Fthat Burnham will have to plug that
OL,19,Fspending gap anyway whether it's more
OL,20,Fdepartmental cuts or tax rises.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
